Dear Investor,

				Planning for your current or future financial goals can be a daunting task. Whether you are a young investor or retiree, a new parent or a single  
				parent, supporting a growing family or an empty nester, National Planning Corporation® (NPC®) and your Investment 
				Professional can help make reaching your most important goals a reality.
			

				NPC's industry-leading technology, vast breadth and depth of product selection, rigorous due diligence process, and experienced Home Office team 
				who views each Investment Professionals' success as our own success, help to make our affiliated Investment Professionals among the top in the 
				financial services industry.
			

				In addition, our unique commitment to proactively requesting and incorporating Investment Professionals' feedback on the ways that we can better 
				serve them, and by extension you, enables us to continuously raise the bar in delivering products and services to help you meet your financial 
				objectives. Thank you for giving us the opportunity to serve you through your NPC Investment Professional.
			

