National Planning Corporation: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 10:34 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of National Planning Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
National Planning Corporation operates as a broker-dealer and registered investment adviser that serves independent financial advisers in the United States. It provides access to securities products and investment advisory services through independent investment professionals. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Santa Monica, California. National Planning Corporation operates as a subsidiary of National Planning Holdings, Inc.


401 Wilshire BoulevardSuite 1100Santa Monica, CA 90401United StatesFounded in 1998



Phone: 888-711-6720

Fax: 877-711-3631

www.natplan.com







